# Project Context

Read `PROJECT_PARAMETERS.md` at the repository root before any task.

Respect:

- `PROJECT_LANGUAGE` — all project artifacts in this language only (it or en, never mixed)
- `CLIENT_NAME` — default Internal
- `VALIDATION_GATE_ENABLED` and `VALIDATION_THRESHOLD`
- `MILESTONE_LIST` when linking REQ to milestones
- Module parameters for the area/module being edited

Target structure: Design / Code / Test with areas of intervention.
